label: uncl3035
comment: Code giving specific meaning to a party.

values.label: Party to be billed (AAR Accounting rule 11)
values.comment: Party to be billed in accordance with AAR Accounting rule 11.

values.label: Buyer's agent/representative
values.comment: Third party who arranged the purchase of merchandise on behalf of the actual buyer.

values.label: Declarant's agent/representative
values.comment: Any natural or legal person who makes a declaration to an official body on behalf of another natural or legal person, where legally permitted (CCC).

values.label: Transit principal
values.comment: Natural or legal person responsible for the satisfactory performance of a Customs transit operation. Source: CCC.

values.label: Agent
values.comment: (3196) Party authorized to act on behalf of another party. Synonym: Representative.

values.label: Transit principal's agent/representative
values.comment: Agent acting on behalf of the transit principal (CCC).

values.label: Successful job applicant
values.comment: Person who has been chosen for a job.

values.label: Party issuing mutually agreed codes
values.comment: The party which has issued all mutually agreed codes used in the message.

values.label: Acknowledgement recipient
values.comment: Party to whom acknowledgement should be sent.

values.label: Principal responsible party
values.comment: (3340) Party accepting liability for goods held or moving (e.g. transit) under a Customs authorization and - when applicable - a guarantee.

values.label: Authorized official
values.comment: Employee of a company or firm authorized to act on behalf of that company or firm e.g. to make a Customs declaration.

values.label: Approved importer
values.comment: Person or company which is authorised by the relevant Customs authority to import goods without payment all taxes or specific taxes at the point of entry into the country.

values.label: Account of
values.comment: Party account is assigned to.

values.label: Accepting party
values.comment: (3336) Party accepting goods, products, services, etc.

values.label: Approved consignor
values.comment: Person or company approved by the relevant authority in the country to pack and export specific goods under Customs supervision.

values.label: Authorized exporter
values.comment: Exporter authorized/approved by Customs for special Customs procedures e.g. simplified procedure.

values.label: Account servicing financial institution
values.comment: Identifies the financial institution servicing the account(s).

values.label: Authorized importer
values.comment: Importer authorized/approved by Customs for special Customs procedures e.g. simplified procedure.

values.label: Authorized trader (transit)
values.comment: Trader authorized/approved by Customs for special transit procedures e.g. simplified procedure.

values.label: Authorizing official
values.comment: Party that has delegated the authority to take a certain action on behalf of a company or agency.

values.label: Applicant's bank
values.comment: (3234) Financial institution which is requested to issue the documentary credit.

values.label: Authenticating party
values.comment: Party which certifies that a document is authentic.

values.label: Animal being investigated
values.comment: Animal being investigated.

values.label: Issuing bank
values.comment: [3320] Financial institution which issues the documentary credit, if the applicant's bank is not acting as the issuing bank.

values.label: Contact bank 1
values.comment: Identifies an additional bank which must be informed of certain aspects of the message.

values.label: Contact bank 2
values.comment: Identifies an additional bank which must be informed of certain aspects of the message.

values.label: Booking agent
values.comment: Party acting as a booking office for transport and forwarding services.

values.label: Buyer bank identification

values.label: Negotiating bank
values.comment: Financial institution to whom a negotiable documentary credit is directed.

values.label: Documentary credit reimbursing bank
values.comment: [3350] A financial institution which reimburses documentary credit.

values.label: Beneficiary's bank
values.comment: (3422) Identifies the account servicer for the beneficiary or the payee.

values.label: Employer
values.comment: A party that keeps a person in service for payment.

values.label: Previous employer
values.comment: Previous employer of a person(s).

values.label: Buyer's financial institution
values.comment: Financial institution designated by buyer to make payment.

values.label: Release to party
values.comment: Party to which the goods or container(s) is (are) to be released.

values.label: Financial institution
values.comment: Party acting as financial institution.

values.label: Bill of lading recipient
values.comment: Party to receive B/L.

values.label: Insured

values.label: Insurance beneficiary
values.comment: Party which benefits from insurance coverage.

values.label: Broker or sales office
values.comment: Party acting in the name of the seller as broker or as sales office.

values.label: Building site purchaser
values.comment: Party at the building site responsible for the purchasing of goods and services for that particular site.

values.label: Cheque drawn bank
values.comment: Identifies the bank on which the cheque should be drawn, as instructed by the ordering customer.

values.label: Bill and ship to
values.comment: Party receiving goods and relevant invoice.

values.label: Party to be billed for other than freight (bill to)
values.comment: Party receiving invoice excluding freight costs.

values.label: Service bureau
values.comment: Party carrying out service bureau processing work, (e.g. a payroll bureau).

values.label: Member
values.comment: Member of a group (e.g. of a group of persons or a service scheme).

values.label: Borrower
values.comment: A person who acquires something temporarily with the promise or intention of returning.

values.label: Building site engineer
values.comment: Party at the building site responsible for engineering matters for that particular site.

values.label: Buyer
values.comment: [3002] Party to which merchandise or services are sold.

values.label: Building site forwarder
values.comment: Party at the building site responsible for forwarding the received goods on that particular site.

values.label: In care of party no. 1
values.comment: A person taking responsibility on behalf of party no. 1.

values.label: In care of party no. 2
values.comment: A person taking responsibility on behalf of party no. 2.

values.label: Carrier
values.comment: [3126] Party undertaking or arranging transport of goods between named points.

values.label: Customs broker
values.comment: Agent or representative or a professional Customs clearing agent who deals directly with Customs on behalf of the importer or exporter (CCC).

values.label: Claimant
values.comment: Party who claims goods or insurance.

values.label: Agent's bank
values.comment: Bank of the agent.

values.label: Ceding company
values.comment: Company which cedes something to someone.

values.label: Container operator/lessee
values.comment: Party to whom the possession of specified property (e.g. container) has been conveyed for a period of time in return for rental payments.

values.label: Carrier's agent
values.comment: [3052] Party authorized to act for or on behalf of carrier.

values.label: Connecting carrier
values.comment: Owner or operator of a transportation conveyance to which goods in a given transaction will be transferred.

values.label: Commission processor
values.comment: Party who provides extra treatment to goods on commission base.

values.label: Previous member
values.comment: Previous member of a group of persons or a service scheme.

values.label: Empty equipment despatch party
values.comment: Party from whose premises empty equipment will be or has been despatched.

values.label: Container location party
values.comment: Party from whose premises container will be or has been despatched.

values.label: Customs
values.comment: Identification of customs authority relevant to the transaction or shipment.

values.label: Consignee
values.comment: [3132] Party to which goods are consigned.

values.label: Cash pool top account servicing financial institution
values.comment: Identification of a financial institution servicing the top account of a cash pool.

values.comment: Identification of a financial institution servicing the level account of a cash pool.

values.label: Cash pool sub-account servicing financial institution
values.comment: Identification of a financial institution servicing the sub-account of a cash pool.

values.comment: Identification of the Head Office within a company.

values.label: Intermediate level parent company
values.comment: Identifies an intermediate parent company.

values.label: Transshipment party
values.comment: A party responsible for transshipment.

values.label: Quotation requesting party
values.comment: Party sending a request for a quotation.

values.label: Party maintaining the codes used in the message
values.comment: The party which maintains the codes used in the message.

values.label: Party maintaining the identifiers used in the message
values.comment: The party which maintains the identifiers used in the message.

values.label: Dispatcher
values.comment: An individual responsible for sending something to a destination.

values.label: Submitter of sample
values.comment: An entity responsible for the submission of a sample.

values.label: Institutional provider
values.comment: The institution providing the service.

values.comment: Health care provider that has primary responsibility for patient.

values.comment: Health care provider that admitted the patient.

values.comment: Health care provider that referred patient to current provider of services.

values.label: Supervising health care provider
values.comment: Health care provider that supervised the rendering of a service.

values.label: Party providing financing
values.comment: Identifies the party providing the financing.

values.label: Convoying party
values.comment: Party designated to escort the transported goods.

values.label: Nominated bank
values.comment: Identifies the nominated bank.

values.label: Family member
values.comment: Identifies a family member.

values.label: Co-participant
values.comment: Identifies another party who participates in an activity.

values.label: Involved party
values.comment: Party which is involved in an activity.

values.label: Assigner
values.comment: Identifies the entity who assigns.

values.label: Registered principal
values.comment: An individual who is registered as a principal for an entity.

values.comment: (3470) Freight payer is a third party acting on behalf of the consignor.

values.label: Freight payer on behalf of the consignee
values.comment: (3470) Freight payer is a third party acting on behalf of the consignee.

values.label: Party responsible for disinfection
values.comment: Party responsible for performing disinfection operations.

values.label: Party responsible for refueling
values.comment: Party responsible for performing refueling operations.

values.label: Party to receive certificate of compliance
values.comment: Party acting for or on behalf of seller in matters concerning compliance.

values.label: Advising bank
values.comment: [3190] Identifies the financial institution used by the issuing bank to advise the documentary credit.

values.label: Reimbursing bank
values.comment: Identifies the financial institution through which the reimbursement is to be effected.

values.label: Advise through bank
values.comment: Identifies the financial institution through which the advising bank is to advise.

values.label: Charges payer at destination
values.comment: Party, other than the ordering party, which has to pay the charges concerning the destination operations.

values.label: Means of transport charterer
values.comment: Charterer of the means of transport.

values.label: Excise party
values.comment: Party to whom excise must be paid.

values.label: Copy report to
values.comment: Party receiving a copy of a report.

values.label: Related healthcare party
values.comment: A healthcare party related to the subject.

values.label: Clinical information provider
values.comment: Party providing clinical information.

values.label: Service requester
values.comment: Party requesting a service.

values.label: Patient admitted by
values.comment: Party who admitted a patient.

values.label: Patient discharged to
values.comment: The party who receives the discharged patient.

values.label: Patient hosted by
values.comment: The party hosting the patient.

values.label: Prescriber's contact person
values.comment: Contact person for the prescriber.

values.label: Cheque order
values.comment: Party to which the cheque will be ordered, when different from the beneficiary.

values.label: Empty equipment return party
values.comment: Party to whose premises empty equipment will be or has been returned.

values.label: Consolidator
values.comment: Party consolidating various consignments, payments etc.

values.label: Consignee to be specified
values.comment: The party to be identified at a later time as the consignee.

values.comment: The company to which containers have to be returned.

values.comment: Party to which the vessel shall be delivered.

values.comment: Owner of equipment (container, etc.).

values.comment: Party authorized to act on behalf of the consignee.

values.comment: IATA cargo agent entitled to commission.

values.comment: [3336] Party which, by contract with a carrier, consigns or sends goods with the carrier, or has them conveyed by him. Synonym: shipper, sender.

values.label: Available with bank (documentary credits)
values.comment: Financial institution with whom the documentary credit is available.

values.label: Distributor branch
values.comment: The affiliate of a retailer or distributor.

values.label: Despatch charge payer
values.comment: Party, other than the ordering party, which has to pay the charges concerning the despatch operations.

values.label: Prescription database owner
values.comment: Organisation or person owning a prescription database.

values.label: Original prescriber
values.comment: The doctor who issued the original prescription.

values.label: Temporary employee
values.comment: A person employed on a temporary basis.

values.label: Designer
values.comment: A party who designs.

values.label: Quotation delivered to
values.comment: Party to whom the quotation is to be or has been delivered.

values.label: Developer
values.comment: A party who develops.

values.label: Test execution party
values.comment: The party performing a test.

values.label: Party to receive refund
values.comment: Party to whom a refund is given.

values.label: Authorised issuer of prescription
values.comment: Party authorised to issue a prescription.

values.label: Authorised dispenser of medicine
values.comment: Organisation or person authorised to dispense medicine.

values.label: Documentary credit account party's bank
values.comment: Bank of the documentary credit account party.

values.label: Report responsible party
values.comment: The party or person taking responsibility for a report.

values.label: Initial sender

values.label: The party authorising the original prescription
values.comment: The party authorising the issuer of the original prescription.

values.label: Applicant
values.comment: A party who applies for something.

values.label: Meter reader

values.label: Alternate electronic business contact
values.comment: Code specifying a party who serves as a business entity's alternate contact for matters related to electronic business.

values.label: Alternate government business contact
values.comment: Code specifying a party who serves as a business entity's alternate contact for matters related to doing business with the government.

values.label: Grid operator

values.comment: Party responsible for the management of the location.

values.label: Group leader

values.comment: Identification of freight forwarder giving services to the consignee.

values.comment: The movement of a passenger from one country to another via the territory of an intermediate country for which no entry is intended.

values.label: Energy production imbalance responsible party
values.comment: A party who can be brought to rights, legally and financially, for any imbalance between energy sold and produced for all associated metering points.

values.comment: A party that is responsible for settlement of the difference between planned and realised quantities.

values.label: Transmission capacity allocator
values.comment: A party managing the allocation of transmission capacity.

values.label: Depositor
values.comment: Party depositing goods, financial payments or documents.

values.label: Metered data aggregator
values.comment: A party responsible for aggregation of metered data.

values.label: Party connected to grid

values.label: Profile maintenance party
values.comment: A party that maintains profiles.

values.label: Stowaway

values.label: Meat cutter

values.label: Non-vessel operating carrier
values.comment: A carrier that does not operate the vessel.

values.label: Stuffing address
values.comment: Address where cargo is loaded into the transport equipment e.g. container. Synonyms; vanning address / place of vanning.

values.comment: Party responsible for mooring the vessel at the berth in the port. Synonym: Boatmen.

values.label: Pilotage service provider
values.comment: Party responsible for the pilotage of the vessel.

values.label: Berth towage service provider
values.comment: Party responsible for towing the vessel to/from the berth in the port.

values.label: Agent/representative, direct representation
values.comment: Party authorised to act in the name and on behalf of another person.

values.label: Agent/representative, indirect representation
values.comment: Party authorised to act in its own name but on behalf of another person.

values.label: Stevedore
values.comment: A party which handles the loading and unloading of marine vessels from several terminals.

values.label: Shipper
values.comment: Party responsible for the shipment of goods.

values.label: Source data pool
values.comment: A data pool that supports the functionality required by a data source such as data loading, publication, notification, registration, etc.

values.label: Brand owner

values.label: Cockpit crew

values.label: Cabin crew
values.comment: Crew members operating in passenger cabin.

values.label: Airline operations management, not in cockpit
values.comment: Personnel of the airline operations management department positioned outside the cockpit.

values.label: Cargo non-cockpit crew and/or non-crew personnel
values.comment: Employees of the carrier, cargo groomers, or special cargo handlers, that are not authorized to ride in the cockpit.

values.label: Pilots seated outside cockpit
values.comment: Pilots currently not in charge of flying the aircraft and not present in the cockpit.

values.label: Commercial verifier

values.label: Authorized issuer

values.label: Documentary credit applicant

values.label: Bank for deposit of duties/taxes/fees
values.comment: Bank that is authorized to receive the deposit for duties, taxes, and fees.

values.label: Company security officer (IMO Circular MSC 1130)
values.comment: The company security officer as described in IMO Circular MSC 1130.

values.label: Distiller

values.label: Drayman/lighterman
values.comment: The bonded (insured) party that moves goods within port limits.

values.label: Exhibitor
values.comment: The party who offers items for exhibit or show.

values.label: Feedlot

values.label: Government official
values.comment: A person appointed to some position of responsibility or authority in the government.

values.label: Government service requestor
values.comment: The party requesting inspection, grading, or other government service.

values.label: Crop grower

values.label: Operator of property, registered

values.label: Organic growth certifier, accredited

values.label: Party holding Certificate of Financial Responsibility
values.comment: The party holding the Certificate of Financial Responsibility (COFR).

values.label: Vehicle owner

values.label: Manufacturer of equipment

values.label: Article information responsible party

values.label: Price information responsible party
values.comment: The party responsible for price information.

values.comment: A party providing logistic services for another party (e.g re-packing suppliers products).

values.label: Fattener

values.comment: Party which provides breeding service.

values.label: Engineer, consultant

values.label: Project coordination office
values.comment: Party responsible for technical coordination of works.

values.label: Engineer, measurement

values.label: Controller, quality
